-- Hidary Discusses Social Media Tracking (Audio)
-- B y
-- 2012-02-24T13:42:02Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-24/hidary-discusses-social-media-tracking-audio-.html
Jack Hidary, chairman of 
RealTimeMonitor.com, discusses the tracking of products, people 
and events in social media, as they are being mentioned by 
consumers.  Hidary talked with Bloomberg's  Kathleen Hays  and 
Vonnie Quinn on "The Hays Advantage" on Bloomberg Radio on 
February 22, 2012.  (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 24:18
 